 | title=A Subaru/Suprime-Cam wide-field survey of globular cluster populations around M87 - I. Observation, data analysis and luminosity function | journal=[[Monthly_Notices_of_the_Royal_Astronomical_Society|Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society]] | volume=373 | issue=2 | pages=588–600 | date=2006 | bibcode=2006MNRAS.373..588T |arxiv = astro-ph/0609067 }}</ref>這些星團的大小分佈和銀河系相似，多數[[有效半徑|有效半徑]]為1〜6秒差距之間。M87裡的星團大小隨著距離核心越遠而漸增。<ref name="#16"/>2014年首度觀測發現到的超高速球狀星團{{le|HVGC-1|HVGC-1}}，就正在從M87星系逃逸出走。<ref>{{cite journal |title= A Globular Cluster Toward M87 with a Radial Velocity < -1000 km/s: The First Hypervelocity Cluster |author=Nelson Caldwell | author2=Jay Strader | author3=Aaron J. Romanowsky | author4=Jean P. Brodie | author5=Ben Moore | author6=Jurg Diemand | author7=Davide Martizzi |date= 25 February 2014 |bibcode= 2014ApJ...787L..11C |arxiv= 1402.6319 |doi=10.1088/2041-8205/787/1/L11}}</ref>這項發現表示，在M87核心的是兩個超大黑洞，而不是一個。這兩個超大質量黑洞是源自於很久以前的兩個星系之碰撞，結果二星系合併成單一巨大星系。<ref>{{Cite journal | author=Aguilar.D.A | display-authors=etal | title=Entire Star Cluster Thrown Out of its Galaxy | journal=Harvard-Smithsonian Center for Astrophysics | url=http://www.cfa.harvard.edu/news/2014-09 | access-date=2016-05-31 | archive-date=2014-04-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140430231637/http://www.cfa.harvard.edu/news/2014-09 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

M87裡的組成還包括超緻密[[矮星系|矮星系]]，它與球狀星團類似，但直徑在10秒差距（33光年）以上，這比球狀星團最大不超過3秒差距（10光年）之上限大得多。目前還不清楚超緻密矮星系的性質，是否為M87所捕獲的矮星系，或是另一類新的巨大球狀星團。M87有數以千計的球狀星團，其中近百個是超緻密矮星系。<ref>{{cite journal|author=Zhang, Hong-Xin; Peng, Eric W.; Côté, Patrick; Liu, Chengze; Ferrarese, Laura; Cuillandre, Jean-Charles; Caldwell, Nelson; Gwyn, Stephen D. J.; Jordán, Andrés; Lançon, Ariane; Li, Biao; Muñoz, Roberto P.; Puzia, Thomas H.; Bekki, Kenji; Blakeslee, John P.; Boselli, Alessandro; Drinkwater, Michael J.; Duc, Pierre-Alain; Durrell, Patrick; Emsellem, Eric; Firth, Peter; Sánchez-Janssen, Rubén|date=2015|title=The Next Generation Virgo Cluster Survey. VI. The Kinematics of Ultra-compact Dwarfs and Globular Clusters in M87|journal=The Astrophysical Journal|volume=802|issue=1|pages=26|doi=10.1088/0004-637X/802/1/30| bibcode=2015ApJ...802...30Z| id = 30|arxiv = 1501.03167 }}</ref>

